
Vue developer roadmap

HTML
	  Basics of HTML 
	  Semantic HTML
	  Dividing page into sections and structuring the DOM properly

CSS
	  Basics of CSS
	  Grid and Flexbox
	  Responsive Web Design and Media Queries

JS 
	  Syntax and basic operations
	  DOM manipulation
	  Hoisting, Event bubbling, prototyping
	  AJAX (XHR)
	  ECMA Script 6+, new features

General development skills
	  Git, Github, Gitlab
	  Http(s) protocol
	  Learn to search for solutions
	  Terminal usage
	  Data structures and algorithms
	  Design patterns

Vue
	Build tools
		  Package managers
			  npm
			  yarn
		    Webpack
	Task runners
			  npm scripts

  Styling
		  CSS preprocessors
			  SASS
			  PostCSS
		  CSS frameworks
			  Tailwind
		  CSS in JS
			  Single file components
 
  State management
		  Component state
		  Vuex
			  Data persistence
				  vuex-persist
				  vuex-persistedstate
			  vuex-loading
			  vuex-shared-mutations

  Type checkers
		  Prop types
		  TypeScript

  Routing
		  vue-router

  API clients
		  GraphQL
			  Apollo
		  Rest
			  fetch (native)
			  axios

  Utility libraries
		  Lodash
		  Moment

  Testing
		  E2E testing	
			  Selenium
			  Cypress
			  Puppeteer
			  Cucumber.js
		  Jest
		  Vue test utils
		  Karma

  i18n
		  vue-i18n
	
  Server side rendering
		  nuxt.js
	
  Desktop
		  electron

